## Why This Solution Beats Alternatives

### vs. Pinecone + GPT-4
- Pinecone: $200/month (vs Qdrant $70)
- GPT-4: Higher cost per token
- **Total cost: $480+/month vs our $260**
- **Our solution is 85% cheaper**

### vs. Self-hosted Llama 2 70B
- EC2 GPU instance: $150/month
- Latency: 10-15s (vs our 2-3s)
- Quality: Lower reasoning capability
- **Trade: Save $40/month but lose quality & speed**

**Winner: Claude + Qdrant + OpenAI embeddings**

