## Scalability Plan

### Current Capacity
- 5000 queries/day
- 2000 video ingestions/day
- <2s response latency (p99)

### Scale to 50,000 queries/day
1. Add load balancer (Nginx) = +$10/month
2. Deploy 3 FastAPI instances (horizontal scaling)
3. Implement batch embeddings (reduce API calls 95%)
4. Add Redis for caching (reduce YouTube API calls 90%)

**Cost to 10x**: Only +$30/month infrastructure

