## Deployment

### Local
```bash
docker run -p 6333:6333 qdrant/qdrant:latest
python backend.py
npm run dev
```

### Production (AWS ECS)
- Use docker-compose for multi-container orchestration
- Store secrets in AWS Secrets Manager
- Set up CloudWatch monitoring
- Auto-scaling policy: CPU > 70% → add instance

